          "text": "Giardia lamblia"
        },
        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "Ascaris lumbricoides"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "Giardia lamblia",
      "explanation": "Giardiasis is caused by Giardia lamblia, a protozoan parasite that infects the small intestine.",
      "difficulty": "medium"
    },
    {
